Subject: [PATCH] Cavium T81: SPI: Enabled support for 32-bit SPI flash

This is needed for the Interface Masters Sierra board.

Signed-off-by: Aaron Williams <aaron.williams@cavium.com>

---
 configs/t81_defconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/configs/t81_defconfig b/configs/t81_defconfig
index 730fd362ed..70621bfaae 100644
--- a/configs/t81_defconfig
+++ b/configs/t81_defconfig
@@ -77,3 +77,4 @@ CONFIG_SYS_I2C_THUNDERX_SLAVE_ADDR=0x77
 CONFIG_ENV_VARS_UBOOT_CONFIG=y
 CONFIG_OF_LIBFDT=y
 CONFIG_OF_BOARD=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_4BAIS=y
